# iOS Platform Rules

## Standalone context

This rule is the implementation anchor for the iOS repo. When working via the monorepo, also see `portent/.cursor/rules/platform/ios-always.mdc` for project-level context.

See `docs/agents/agent-ios.md` for full agent definition. This rule applies when working in `apps/ios/`.

## Stack

Swift 6, SwiftUI, MVVM, @Observable, URLSession, Codable. Targets iOS 26+ and macOS Catalyst.

## Conventions

- Use `FeatureView` / `FeatureViewContents` pattern per `.cursor/rules/ui/agent-ios.mdc`
- Use `ViewState<T>` (or `UiState<T>`) for screen state: Loading, Success(T), Error, Refreshing(T)
- Domain layer has no SwiftUI/UIKit imports
- Never log secrets, tokens, or PII

